      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCESS ADA (1) sizzled around this track over 520m in 29.61 for a 1.5 lengths win. Should be in this for a long way. TARAWI BRUMBY (7) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished second (29.87) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Has a good record at this journey. Must be included in calculations. ANNIE'S RUPEE (3) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 29.75 beating TARAWI BRUMBY. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Will go close again if runs up to latest. EUREKA MAC (8) is a chance after winning last time.",
